OL,3,C'Screams of horror' heard as man
OL,4,Cstabbed friend on Christmas Eve
OL,6,FA man killed his best friend in a
OL,7,F"frenzied attack" hours after
OL,8,Fresearching neck anatomy online, a
OL,9,Fcourt has heard.
OL,11,FDylan Thomas, 24, is accused of
OL,12,Fmurdering William Bush, 23, who died
OL,13,Fon December 24 last year in Cardiff.
OL,14,FMr Bush suffered 37 separate injuries
OL,15,Fin the attack which, the court heard,
OL,16,Fwas inflicted by two separate knives.
OL,18,FThomas, previously of Llandaff,
OL,19,Fadmitted manslaughter on the grounds
OL,20,Fof diminished responsibility at a
OL,21,Fhearing last week but denies murder.
