OL,6,FHe appeared before Cardiff Crown Court
OL,7,Fby video link from a psychiatric
OL,8,Fhospital on Wednesday.
OL,10,FOn the opening day of the trial at
OL,11,FCardiff Crown Court, the jury were
OL,12,Ftold that Thomas and Mr Bush had met
OL,13,Fas schoolboys at Christ College Brecon.
OL,15,FThey later moved in to a house owned
OL,16,Fby the defendant's grandparents on
OL,17,FChapel Street in the Llandaff area of
OL,18,FCardiff.
