OL,6,FMr Bush, who was 23 when he died, was
OL,7,Fdescribed as "well liked and popular,
OL,8,Fathletic and a keen golfer", and was
OL,9,Fsaid to be looking forward to starting
OL,10,Fa new job in 2024 and moving in with
OL,11,Fhis girlfriend.
OL,13,FDylan Thomas was described by
OL,14,Fprosecutor Greg Bull KC as "something
OL,15,Fof a loner" with "few friends."
OL,17,F"He relied heavily on William Bush for
OL,18,Fsupport", Mr Bull told the court, with
OL,19,FMr Bush said to have given Thomas -
OL,20,Fwho couldn't drive - regular lifts in
OL,21,Fhis car.
