OL,6,FBut in the months leading up to the
OL,7,Fattack, the court heard, the
OL,8,F"dynamics" of the relationship between
OL,9,Fthe two men changed.
OL,11,FIn October 2023, Mr Bush informed his
OL,12,Fgirlfriend that the defendant had told
OL,13,Fhim: "I thought about killing you and
OL,14,FI wondered what would happen if I did
OL,15,Fcertain things."
OL,17,FMr Bush's girlfriend told police that
OL,18,Fhe had taken the comment seriously,
OL,19,Fbarricading his door while he slept.
