OL,6,FMr Bull described events leading up to
OL,7,Fthe incident, saying "screams of
OL,8,Fhorror" coming from the house during
OL,9,Fthe attack could be heard from the
OL,10,Fstreet.
OL,12,FMr Bull told the court that in the
OL,13,Fdays before the attack, Dylan Thomas
OL,14,Fwent to his grandparents' house in the
OL,15,FVale of Glamorgan for Christmas.
