OL,3,C'Screams of horror' heard as man
OL,4,Cstabbed friend on Christmas Eve
OL,6,FBut after appearing normal during a
OL,7,Ffamily lunch, the defendant seemed
OL,8,F"unable to settle" later in the day.
OL,9,FThe following night, the court was
OL,10,Ftold, Thomas carried out online
OL,11,Fsearches of the anatomy of the jugular
OL,12,Fvein in the neck.
OL,14,FIn the early hours of the morning, he
OL,15,Fsent text messages to William Bush
OL,16,Fsaying "I need to see you before I go"
OL,17,Fand "What time are you leaving?",
OL,18,Fbefore trying to book an Uber taxi to
OL,19,Ftake him back to the property the two
OL,20,Fshared.
