OL,6,FThe next morning, Mr Bull told the
OL,7,Fjury, the defendant persuaded his
OL,8,Fgrandmother to drive him to Cardiff
OL,9,Fbecause, he said, he wanted to walk
OL,10,Fhis dog.
OL,12,FThey arrived at the property at
OL,13,F11:15am. William Bush was still there
OL,14,Fahead of setting off to spend
OL,15,FChristmas with his family in Brecon.
