OL,6,FMr Bull said: "The prosecution say
OL,7,FDylan Thomas entered the property,
OL,8,Farmed himself with a kitchen knife and
OL,9,Fand a smaller knife, and went upstairs
OL,10,Fto Mr Bush's bedroom on the second
OL,11,Ffloor.
OL,13,F"The prosecution case is that (Mr
OL,14,FBush) was attacked from behind at
OL,15,Ffirst. If (Mr Bush) had seen Dylan
OL,16,FThomas coming he'd have been easily
OL,17,Fable to overpower him.
