OL,6,F"Dylan Thomas chased William Bush down
OL,7,Fthe stairs until Mr Bush sustained the
OL,8,Ffatal injury and collapsed on the
OL,9,Fpatio."
OL,11,FThe court heard that the victim had
OL,12,Fsuffered 37 separate knife injuries,
OL,13,Fincluding a laceration to his neck and
OL,14,Fa deep wound to the back of his neck.
OL,16,FThere were also injuries to his chest
OL,17,Fand abdomen, and a total of 20 wounds
OL,18,Fto his hands - consistent, the jury
OL,19,Fwas told, with "defence" injuries.
OL,20,FBlood marks were found on the walls
OL,21,Fand stairs of the three bedroom house.
