OL,6,FParamedics were unable to save Mr
OL,7,FBush's life and the cause of death was
OL,8,Flater given as "multiple stab wounds
OL,9,Fto the neck and trunk".
OL,11,FThe court was shown police body-worn
OL,12,Fcamera footage of the moment officers
OL,13,Farrived to at the scene, showing Dylan
OL,14,FThomas with his hands covered in blood.
OL,16,FThomas is seen telling officers that
OL,17,Fhe's been stabbed. An officer asks
OL,18,Fhim: "Where's the person who's done
OL,19,Fthis?" Thomas replies: "He's dead."
