OL,6,FThe defendant was taken to the
OL,7,FUniversity Hospital of Wales for a
OL,8,Ftreatment, where, the court heard, he
OL,9,Fcontinued to claim that William Bush
OL,10,Fhad started the violence, saying Mr
OL,11,FBush had "gone mental" after smoking
OL,12,Fcannabis and attacked him.
OL,14,FHe told another officer: "He was
OL,15,Fhaving one of his episodes. It's been
OL,16,Fhappening for months."
