OL,6,FMr Bull, for the prosecution, told the
OL,7,Fjury that the defence would rely on
OL,8,Fthe evidence of a forensic
OL,9,Fpsychiatrist from Ashworth High Secure
OL,10,FHospital - where Dylan Thomas is being
OL,11,Fheld - that the defendant was
OL,12,Fsuffering from psychosis at the time
OL,13,Fof the attack.
OL,15,FBut Mr Bull said that the court would
OL,16,Fhear from another psychiatric expert
OL,17,Fwhose view was "that the defendant
OL,18,Fknew what he was doing."
