OL,6,F"Taken as a whole, the evidence shows
OL,7,Fa picture of clear thinking that shows
OL,8,Fan intention to inflict really serious
OL,9,Fharm on Mr Bush."
OL,11,FThomas denies murder and is expected
OL,12,Fto defend himself against the charge
OL,13,Fon the grounds of diminished
OL,14,Fresponsibility. The trial continues.
